<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR1h0001-zh-32b446fb" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>孟子今註今譯</title><editor role="translator">Shi Ciyun 史次耘</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>孟子今註今譯</title>臺北：商務印書館，1973</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR1h0001"><title xml:lang="och">孟子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-02-09T19:30:34.718+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR1h0001-start"><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:31:13.441+09:00">『人和禽獸不同旳地方，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:31:56.078+09:00">祗在極微少旳－點．就是人旳天性具有仁義罷了。，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:31:59.592+09:00">往往把它抛棄掉，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:32:07.498+09:00">君子是隨時知道仁義可貴而保存它。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:32:19.482+09:00">大舜能明辨一切事物旳理性，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:32:50.193+09:00">察知做人的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:33:02.582+09:00">完全順着天性旳仁義做去，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-23a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-09T19:51:10.306+09:00">並不是認爲仁義有利於已而勉強去做呢。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:26:14.368+09:00">孟子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:26:23.743+09:00">『仁義禮智，去求它，就可得着，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:26:29.938+09:00">捨棄它，便要失掉。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:26:34.69+09:00">這個求是有助於得的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:27:42.677+09:00">富貴利達，去求它也有方法，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:28:15.863+09:00">但是想得着卻有命運，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:28:47.552+09:00">這個求是無助於得的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T00:28:45.669+09:00">因爲所求是身外的事物咽°』【章旨】此章特強調「爲仁由己，富貴在天，」</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T01:00:59.901+09:00">孟子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T03:57:06.434+09:00">『一切人倫事物之理，皆具備在我自己旳身上。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T01:01:19.589+09:00">祇要反省自身，眞實不欺，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T01:01:24.107+09:00">這個快樂沒有再比它大的了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T01:01:39.273+09:00">勉強推行恕道，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-11T01:03:16.586+09:00">求仁的途徑，沒有比這頁接近的了。』章旨】此章示人盡性之學：在反求諸己，眞實不欺．，強恕行仁，樂在其中。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:20:02.989+09:00">孟子說：『齊國牛山的樹木，從前是很茂美旳，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:12:12.583+09:00">『齊國牛山的樹木，從前是很茂美旳，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:11:57.85+09:00">祇因鄰近都城的郊外，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:11:48.289+09:00">人們多把它砍伐去，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:11:29.2+09:00">怎能保持它的美茂呢？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:11:15.17+09:00">這山上日夜所生長的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:12:34.313+09:00">雨露所滋潤的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:13:48.442+09:00">並不是沒有芽孽發生出來．</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:14:39.133+09:00">＇可是時喫掉它，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:15:54.3+09:00">所以才像這樣光禿禿旳3．</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:16:29.329+09:00">人見它光禿禿的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:16:35.373+09:00">就以爲它從來沒有長過森林，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:16:49.605+09:00">這難追足山的性嗎？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:17:13.431+09:00">存在人身上旳，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T21:18:03.159+09:00">難道同沒有仁義的心嗎？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:24:30.637+09:00">人之所以放失掉他旳良心，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:25:21.948+09:00">也和斧斤對於樹木一樣，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:25:35.159+09:00">天天砍伐它，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:25:50.721+09:00">還磴培美茂嗎？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:25:58.938+09:00">－個人，日夜所生長的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:28:15.616+09:00">在天明時，沒有和外物接觸以前，神氣清明．＇</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:28:55.347+09:00">他的喜好和厭惡，與常人相近很少。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:30:59.863+09:00">但一到白天，又被所做的行爲把</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:31:10.437+09:00">那清明神氣擾亂亡失了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:31:19.323+09:00">如果－再的擾亂亡失，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:31:33.043+09:00">連那點清明夜氣也不能保存，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:31:41.946+09:00">清明夜氣不能保存，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:31:50.302+09:00">那就和禽獸相差不遠了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:32:00.827+09:00">人們看他和禽獸差不多，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:32:12.972+09:00">便以爲他原來沒有好的才質．，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:32:36.632+09:00">難道這眞是人的本性嗎？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:32:46.247+09:00">所以祇要得到適當的培養，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:32:55.065+09:00">沒有「物不能生長；</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:33:03.666+09:00">假使失去了適當的培養·，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:33:08.625+09:00">沒有一物不消亡。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:33:19.841+09:00">孔子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:33:26.927+09:00">「把握住便能存在，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:33:40.384+09:00">捨棄了就會亡失；</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:34:03.981+09:00">它的進出，沒有定期，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-31a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:34:14.931+09:00">也不知它一定的居處。」</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-32a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-12T23:34:27.131+09:00">這就是說心吧！</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:57:24.575+09:00">告子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:57:35.831+09:00">『凡是有生命旳，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:58:24.548+09:00">孟子說·:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:58:34.214+09:00">『凡是有生命旳，就有這個性，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:58:43.156+09:00">那同白旳東西，統叫做白旳嗎？』</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:58:49.35+09:00">告子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:59:01.994+09:00">『是的。』</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:59:36.816+09:00">孟子說：『白羽旳白，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:59:43.301+09:00">如同白雪旳嗎？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:59:50.404+09:00">白雪旳白，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-9a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T20:59:55.27+09:00">如同白玉旳白嗎？』</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-9a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T21:00:23.655+09:00">告子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T21:00:29.414+09:00">『是旳。』</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T21:00:37.013+09:00">孟子說：『依照這樣說來，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T21:00:42.623+09:00">那末犬旳本性</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T21:00:52.905+09:00">如同牛旳本性，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-16T21:01:11.085+09:00">牛旳本性，如同人旳本性嗎？』【章旨】此章闢告子論「生之謂性」有誤。蓋物性殊異，惟人性本善，與生俱來。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-49a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:21.091+09:00">孟子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-49a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:25.796+09:00">『捉心沒有比減少嗜欲更好了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-49a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:32.135+09:00">如能咸少欲念，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-49a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:37.091+09:00">卽便失去本心時，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-49a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:43.87+09:00">那也很少旳；</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-49a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:50.887+09:00">如果欲念太多，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-49a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:57.95+09:00">叩吏保有本心時</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-50a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-18T23:47:59.299+09:00">，那也是很少旳。』【章旨】此草示人捉心之耍訣仃寡欲。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:20:51.661+09:00">孟子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:21:01.025+09:00">『不要做自家本心所不願做事，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:21:10.035+09:00">不要想那自己本心所不願想旳私欲。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T00:21:26.535+09:00">做人就是這樣罷了。』【章旨】此章係就孔子恕道之旨推闡之。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T18:23:23.18+09:00">孟子說：『君子做學問，必定用方法深入到所研究的學問裏，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-16a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T18:25:02.892+09:00">希望默識心通，自然地領悟得眞理．，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-16a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T18:25:40.586+09:00">能自然地領悟得眞理，心就會安適的住在那裏．，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-16a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T18:25:52.073+09:00">能安適的居住那裏，一切行事，皆可藉助於它。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-16a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T18:26:34.969+09:00">一切行事皆可藉助它，那麼反用起來，或左或右，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-16a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T18:26:42.188+09:00">到處都可遇到本源，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-17a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-20T18:27:16.89+09:00">所以君子希望默識心通，能有然地領悟得眞理。』【章旨】比章示人治學之方法，當以心得爲主。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:42:55.315+09:00">孟子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:43:03.402+09:00">『嘴吧想吃好味，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:43:08.334+09:00">脹睛想看美色，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:43:14.763+09:00">耳朶喜聽音樂，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:43:19.124+09:00">鼻子喜聞香味，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:43:25.212+09:00">四肢都想安逸，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:43:28.954+09:00">這都是人旳本性；</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:44:51.139+09:00">但能不能夠享受這些？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:45:21.845+09:00">但是君子不認爲這是天性，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:45:49.312+09:00"/><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:46:08.756+09:00">道義對於君臣，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:46:15.324+09:00">禮節對於賓主，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:46:23.427+09:00">智惹對於賢者，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:46:30.042+09:00">聖人的對於天道，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:46:36.087+09:00">一般人都以爲是命定旳，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-31a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:46:50.217+09:00">事實上卻存於本性中；</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_014-32a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-21T02:47:54.125+09:00">所以君子總在本性上追求，不說那是命定旳。』【章旨】此章言君子盡性立命之學，尊德樂道，不事口體之安逸。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:48:43.427+09:00">天下人耍研究萬物旳本性，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:48:50.358+09:00">必須以自然爲本。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:05.223+09:00">討嫌那些小聰明的人，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:17.531+09:00">他們專好違反自然，都是穿鑿附會，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:26.214+09:00">如果聰明人</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:36.37+09:00">能像禹引水流行一樣，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:47.443+09:00">我就不會討嫌他們了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:57.939+09:00">禹引水流行，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:50:08.679+09:00">全是順着水旳目然趨勢，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:50:58.395+09:00">那麼他旳聰明也夠大了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:08.545+09:00">譬如天是那樣旳方同，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:15.251+09:00">星辰是那樣旳遠，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:26.877+09:00">假使求着它運行旳常軌，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:36.47+09:00">雖是千年久遠旳冬全，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-32a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:45.095+09:00">都可以坐着推算出來旳。』【章旨】此章言大智，莫非順應自然，以推及事物之原理；而小智穿鑿，往往戕害事物之本性。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-20a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:28:11.64+09:00">徐子問孟子道：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-20a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:28:19.085+09:00">『從前孔子屢次稱贊水說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-20a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:28:36.722+09:00">「水啊！</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-20a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:28:45.054+09:00">水啊！」</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-20a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T03:40:58.041+09:00">Das Wasser Die Stelle bezieht sich wohl auf Lun Yü IX, 16, obwohl der Wortlaut abweicht.!‹</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T03:41:09.001+09:00">Was hat er am Wasser Besonderes gefunden?«</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:29:22.133+09:00">孟子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:29:29.98+09:00">『有源旳水，混混地湧出來，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:29:36.344+09:00">日夜不停地流着，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:29:41.328+09:00">等到流滿了坑陷，然後再繼續向前進行，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T03:41:24.098+09:00">und fließt weiter bis zum Meer.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T03:41:27.861+09:00">So ist es, wenn es einen Ursprung hat.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T03:41:37.961+09:00">Das hat der Meister als Gleichnis genommen.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:30:33.651+09:00">假使沒有本源旳水，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:30:42.49+09:00">那就像七八月間大雨</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:31:07.728+09:00">驟然旳注集，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:31:30.661+09:00">田間大小水溝部漲満了，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:31:35.409+09:00">但雨－停止，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:31:48.539+09:00">它乾涸極快，可以站在旁邊等待着旳。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-21a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:32:53.797+09:00">所以虛名超過了事實，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-22a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-27T02:34:39.468+09:00">君子是認爲可恥旳。』　　【章旨】此章特藉水有本源爲喻，以明君子之學，亦應有其本源，不可作浮光掠影之談。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-03T19:36:51.356+09:00">孟子說：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-03T19:36:58.039+09:00">『有道德旳偉人，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-03T19:37:02.731+09:00">說旳話不一定守信，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-03T19:37:15.44+09:00">做旳事不一定果決，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-14a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-03T19:38:27.627+09:00">但獨以正義爲依歸。』【章旨】此章言大人之言行，皆以義理。</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>